trading and investment strategies at the firm. He was instrumental in the launch
of the firm’s mutual fund family in 2009 and has served as part of the portfolio
management team since 2004. Prior to Astor, Mr. Novak was an equity options
trader for Second City Trading, LLC at the CBOE in Chicago. He has been quoted
by numerous financial media outlets and is a regular panelist at ETF industry
events. Mr. Novak earned his Bachelor of Science in Financial Management from
the Ohio State University.  Mr. Novak is a CAIA charter holder.Deepika Sharma, Director of Investments
